														option(value='1')
															| Bedroom
															option(value='2')
																| Kitchen
																option(value='3')
																	| Bathroom
																	option(value='4')
																		| Living room
												br
												| The most important consideration here is the room's location in the house.
												| If possible, go for a bathroom that doesn't face the front door of your house.
												| With houses on two floors it's better not to have this room above the main entrance to the house.
												| If mirrors are bad in the bedroom they certainly aren't here it's the perfect place for them.
												p
